### Authentication — Manual HTTP Tests
### Run with VS Code REST Client or JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8003

### ── Register a new user ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Test+User&email=manual-test@example.com&password=password123&password_confirmation=password123

### ── Login with valid credentials ────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=alice@demo.test&password=password

### ── Login with INVALID credentials (expect 302 redirect + session error) ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

email=alice@demo.test&password=wrongpassword

### ── Logout ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Replace SESSION_COOKIE with the session cookie from a successful login
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Cookie: laravel_session=SESSION_COOKIE
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_token=CSRF_TOKEN

### ── Access protected route without auth (expect 302 → /login) ──────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Accept: text/html

### ── Access protected route with auth (expect 200) ─────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Cookie: laravel_session=AUTHED_SESSION
Accept: text/html

### ── Attempt to register with duplicate email (expect validation error) ─────
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Another+User&email=alice@demo.test&password=password123&password_confirmation=password123
